// PF1e skill-tap handler.
// Every skill row in 08_skills.rpgs fires
//   on_tap_event = event(name = "skillTap", payload = payload(stat=..., statName=...))
// PF1e skills are rank-based with no proficiency tier, so unlike the pf2e
// `skillTapForward` macro (which branched on edit_mode to either rollStat
// or editSkillProficiency), we just forward to rollStat unconditionally.
// The payload (stat + statName) is preserved by forwardEvent.
mechanic skill_tap(event_names = "skillTap") =
  forwardEvent(new_event_names = ["rollStat"]);
